release_note: Improved the stability of the app.
NEW: You can now send dictations from OD to a specified OneDrive folder via ODP. NEW: Support of iOS15 FIXED: The e mail address for the recipients can be entered correctly.
Fixed the issue that OD did not start on iOS9.

Specification change: Removed the limitation on the number of characters in the domain when manually entering the e mail address in OD. Bug fix: Fixed an issue that the recording start time was when a new file was created instead of the actual start of the recording.
Improved: Changed the display of the options setting when adding additional Recipients.

NOTICE: This is a major version update. Please be sure to backup all existing dictations prior to running the update. NEW: All app users are now required to have an ODDS account. Sign up for a free trail directly from with the app.
NEW: The privacy policy has been updated. Improvement: Improved stability.
New: Support of iOS12.1 New: Olympus Dictation Privacy Policy has been added.
New: Support of the latest FlashAir Card

For all users NEW: Support of iOS8 For ODDS users Improvement: Simpler set up for first time users NEW: Users can now select a recipient typist in the App Improvement: Easily transfer ODDS license to new Smartphone

Ver.1.1.2 Fixed a bug: VCVA Variable Control Voice Actuator malfunction on iOS8 Fixed a bug: Slight delay in stopping a playback on iOS8. Ver. 1.1.1 NEW: Support of FlashAir Class10. Ver. 1.1.0 NEW: Support of iOS7
Ver. 1.1.1 NEW: Support of FlashAir Class10. Ver. 1.1.0 NEW: Support of iOS7
